Privacy Policy

Effective Date: January 26, 2024

Introduction

Welcome to Off-Camp. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the collection, use, and protection of your personal information when you use our mobile application and related services.

Information We Collect

Personal Information:

When you sign up for Off-Camp, we collect your first name, last name, username, and password to create and secure your account.
We may also collect your email address and phone number for communication purposes.
Location Information:

We request permission to access your device's location to provide you with relevant information about bursary funded residences in your area.
How We Use Your Information

Account Creation:

Your personal information is used solely for the purpose of creating and managing your Off-Camp account.
Location-Based Services:

We use your location information to provide you with relevant content, such as mapping bursary funded residences in your vicinity.
Communication:

We may use your email address or phone number to send you important updates, announcements, and notifications related to Off-Camp.
Improving Our Services:

We may analyze user behavior and feedback to enhance and optimize the features and user experience of Off-Camp.
Sharing Your Information

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as described in this Privacy Policy or as required by law.

Security Measures

We take reasonable and appropriate measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

Your Choices

As the app is under development, account information updates are not available. However, you may contact us at the provided email address and phone number to address any concerns or requests related to your personal information.

Research Advisory

While we have verified the legitimacy of the residences and landlords on Off-Camp, we advise users to conduct their own research to ensure their satisfaction and security.

No Subscription or Automated Ads

Our app does not require a subscription, and we do not use automated ads.

Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: offcamp98th@gmail.com
WhatsApp: +27 61 350 0280
Changes to Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated Privacy Policy on the Off-Camp app.

By using Off-Camp, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

